    {
        "content": "<p>guys, problem solved! <a href=\"https://www.kernel.org/doc/html/latest/rust/quick-start.html\">doc</a></p>\n<p>commands:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">LLVM</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">CC</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">clang</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">defconfig</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">LLVM</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">CC</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">clang</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">menuconfig</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"n\">enable</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">option</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Rust</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Support</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">in</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">General</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Setup</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Menu</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">cat</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">config</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">|</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">grep</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">CONFIG_RUST</span>\n\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_RUSTC_VERSION</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">108100</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_RUST_IS_AVAILABLE</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_RUST</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_RUSTC_VERSION_TEXT</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"s\">\"rustc 1.81.0 (eeb90cda1 2024-09-04)\"</span>\n<span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">CONFIG_RUST_FW_LOADER_ABSTRACTIONS</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">not</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">set</span>\n<span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">CONFIG_RUST_PHYLIB_ABSTRACTIONS</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">not</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">set</span>\n<span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">CONFIG_RUST_DEBUG_ASSERTIONS</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">not</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">set</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_RUST_OVERFLOW_CHECKS</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n<span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">CONFIG_RUST_BUILD_ASSERT_ALLOW</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">not</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">set</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>after this:</p>\n<p>rust-analyzer = success<br>\nrusttest = success</p>\n<p><strong>thanks guys.</strong>..</p>\n<p>any tip to build only rust folder ?</p>",
