    {
        "content": "<p>To use syzkaller,I  open these configs below</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Coverage</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">collection</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_KCOV</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n\n<span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Debug</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">info</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">symbolization</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_DEBUG_INFO_DWARF4</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n\n<span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Memory</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">bug</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">detector</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_KASAN</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_KASAN_INLINE</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n\n<span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Required</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Debian</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Stretch</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">and</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">later</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_CONFIGFS_FS</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_SECURITYFS</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Then make LLVM=1<br>\nsomthing error happen</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">scripts</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">Makefile</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">compiler</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">81</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">***</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">unterminated</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">call</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">to</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">function</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">'</span><span class=\"na\">call</span><span class=\"o\">'</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">missing</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"sc\">')'</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"w\">  </span><span class=\"n\">Stop</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"p\">]:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">***</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">home</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">lgt</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">workspace</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">next</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">Makefile</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">369</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">__build_one_by_one</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Error</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n<span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">***</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">[</span><span class=\"n\">Makefile</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"mi\">248</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">__sub</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"p\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Error</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">2</span>\n<span class=\"p\">[.</span><span class=\"n\">config</span><span class=\"p\">](</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">user_uploads</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"mi\">35136</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">FwzkxRuuRSp76TPyH83opvGq</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"p\">.</span><span class=\"n\">config</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Is there some conflict config in rfl or some other reason?</p>",
