    {
        "content": "<p>I use rust Rust-for-Linux/linux -b rust-next,open config_RUST<br>\nit work perfectly without these config</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Coverage</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">collection</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_KCOV</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n\n<span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Debug</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">info</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">symbolization</span><span class=\"p\">.</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_DEBUG_INFO_DWARF4</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n\n<span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Memory</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">bug</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">detector</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_KASAN</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_KASAN_INLINE</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n\n<span class=\"p\">#</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Required</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"k\">for</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Debian</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Stretch</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">and</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">later</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_CONFIGFS_FS</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n<span class=\"n\">CONFIG_SECURITYFS</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"n\">y</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>rust dependence</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">lgt</span><span class=\"o\">@</span><span class=\"n\">dell</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">PowerEdge</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">T640</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"o\">~/</span><span class=\"n\">workspace</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">next</span><span class=\"cp\">$</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">clang</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">--</span><span class=\"n\">version</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Ubuntu</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">clang</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">version</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mf\">21.0.0</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"p\">(</span><span class=\"o\">++</span><span class=\"mi\">20250330053148</span><span class=\"o\">+</span><span class=\"mi\">424</span><span class=\"n\">c8f9217b7</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"o\">~</span><span class=\"n\">exp1</span><span class=\"o\">~</span><span class=\"mf\">20250330173203.1360</span><span class=\"p\">)</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Target</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">x86_64</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">pc</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">gnu</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Thread</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">model</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"nc\">posix</span>\n<span class=\"n\">InstalledDir</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">usr</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">lib</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">llvm</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"mi\">21</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">bin</span>\n<span class=\"n\">lgt</span><span class=\"o\">@</span><span class=\"n\">dell</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">PowerEdge</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">T640</span><span class=\"p\">:</span><span class=\"o\">~/</span><span class=\"n\">workspace</span><span class=\"o\">/</span><span class=\"n\">linux</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">rust</span><span class=\"o\">-</span><span class=\"n\">next</span><span class=\"cp\">$</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">LLVM</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">rustavailable</span>\n<span class=\"n\">Rust</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">is</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">available</span><span class=\"o\">!</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>I build it with</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Rust\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"n\">make</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">LLVM</span><span class=\"o\">=</span><span class=\"mi\">1</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
